title: Fold Org Headings on Startup
tags: @zettel _method orgmode
roam-id: e334818f-77b8-49e7-a8ad-173ec4703f18
type: text/markdown

- globally

``` elisp
;; doom/config.el
(setq org-startup-folded 'overview)
```

- if you want to enable this per file add the following rule on the top of the org file (remove comma)

  ``` org
  #+STARTUP: overview
  ```
